 22873                           ;	Boot Block enable bit
 22874                           ;	BBEN = OFF, Boot block disabled
 22875                           ;	Storage Area Flash enable bit
 22876                           ;	SAFEN = OFF, SAF disabled
 22877                           ;	Background Debugger
